  <div class="block-3">
    <div class="inner-block">
      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Debbie became the Department for Work and Pensions Human Resources (<abbr title="Human Resources">HR</abbr>) Director General in January 2014. Before joining the civil service she served 21 years in the private sector in a variety of <abbr title="Human Resources">HR</abbr> roles in the UK and abroad.</p>

</div>
      </section>

      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_2444">
            <h1 id="director-general-human-resources">Director General, Human Resources</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>The Director General, Human Resources (<abbr title="Human Resources">HR</abbr>), sets the department’s <abbr title="Human Resources">HR</abbr> strategy – aligning this to both the business strategy and <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/civil-service-reform">Civil Service Reform</a>.</p>

</div>
            <div class="read-more">
                <p class="js-hide-other-departments organisations-name-list">
  <a class="organisation-link" href="/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions">Department for Work and Pensions</a>
</p>

            </div>
</section>          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_4968">
            <h1 id="non-executive-director-bpdts">Non-Executive Director, BPDTS</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>BPDTS Ltd is a digital technology company that’s been set up to provide specialist digital technology services to the Department for Work and Pensions (<abbr title="Department for Work and Pensions">DWP</abbr>).</p>

<p>BPDTS’s board sets out the strategy and agrees how operational decisions are taken.</p>

</div>
